author: Xbox
description:
LEGO® Voyagers is out now on Xbox Series X|S

Visit an all-new world in this new co-op adventure from Light Brick Studio, makers of LEGO Builder's Journey 

The journey begins here:
Xbox Series X|S: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/lego-voyagers/9PLJWSWSZPDX

From the makers of LEGO® Builder's Journey comes a new 2-player co-op adventure about friendship and play. When two friends make it their mission to rescue an abandoned spaceship, they embark on a journey beyond their wildest dreams, ultimately learning the value of being connected.

Developed by Light Brick Studio. Published by Annapurna Interactive.

© Annapurna Interactive, 2025

description:
Chaotic co-op city builder Overthrown launches into 1.0 on October 16 with a major new airship update!

Play now in Game Preview and Game Pass for Xbox and PC! 

In Overthrown, you'll lift and throw anything as you build and manage your kingdom in this chaotic city builder for 1-6 players. Harness the power of a soul-stealing crown to defend your citizens from bandits, farm the land, and gather resources.
